These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, pakistani, dutch, australian
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, magic-tricks, traveling, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the dutch##1
2. the nigerian is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the australian is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
5. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | pakistani | australian | dutch |
| Hobby        | photography | magic-tricks   | skydiving | traveling    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, rock-climbing, dancing
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, emerald, apricot, brown
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person who likes apricot is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes blue is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
5. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
6. the person who likes blue is the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | board-games  | card-games  | dancing |
| Color   | brown    | blue | apricot | emerald    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rat, frog, dog
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, green, pink, azure
1. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
2. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
4. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is in an odd position##4
6. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Pet          | dog | frog | rat    | lizard      |
| Color   | pink        | azure     | chestnut | green |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, aristoff, montecristo, alhambra
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, airplane, helicopter, scooter
1. the aristoff-smoker is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the scooter##2
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Cigar         | alhambra | blend | aristoff | montecristo |
| Transport   | helicopter       | bike   | airplane    | scooter  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, dancing, rock-climbing, cooking
4 different games are played: chess, go, scrabble, monopoly
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing go is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4
6. the person playing chess is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | dancing  | reading    | rock-climbing   | cooking       |
| Game   | chess | monopoly | scrabble | go |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, bartender, dressmaker, paramedic
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, aconite, daisy, tulip
1. the person who growsaconite is in an even position##4
2. the paramedic is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the dressmaker is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the analyst##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Job   | dressmaker      | bartender | paramedic | analyst |
| Flower   | tulip | aconite     | poppy  | daisy  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, plum, cranberry, potato
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, lacrosse, weightlifting, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is the person eating lime##1
5. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | lime | potato | cranberry | plum    |
| Sport     | surfing | weightlifting  | cycling     | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, skateboard, subway, scooter
House: victorian, gothic-revival, art-deco, cottage
1. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
2. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
3. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
4. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the cottage house##1
5. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the skateboard##2
6. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
7. the gothic-revival house is between the person driving the trike and the art-deco house##2
8. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Transport   | skateboard | trike      | scooter | subway |
| House   | victorian  | cottage | gothic-revival    | art-deco            |

