.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, aristoff, vegafina, bolivar
City: hannover, rome, new-york, venice
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
2. the prince-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is between the person traveling to rome and the vegafina-smoker##2
4. the person traveling to hannover is in an odd position##4
5. the vegafina-smoker is the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Cigar   | bolivar | aristoff   | prince | vegafina |
| City    | venice     | rome | hannover     | new-york  |

