.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, october, june, august
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, dannemann, montecristo, davidoff
1. the person who's birthday is in december is the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is between the game-smoker and the person who's birthday is in june##2
4. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
5. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Birthday      | october       | june   | december | august |
| Cigar   | montecristo | dannemann | davidoff        | game    |

