.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, pall-mall, old-henry, aristoff
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, pear, kiwi, aristoff-polo
1. the person eating asparagus is in an even position##4
2. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
3. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating aristoff-polo##1
4. the person eating aristoff-polo is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
5. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Cigar   | havana   | aristoff   | pall-mall      | old-henry      |
| Food      | pear | kiwi | aristoff-polo | asparagus |

