.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, climbing, ice-hockey, swimming
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, grey, black, emerald
1. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person who likes black is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is climbing is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who likes grey and the person who likes black##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Sport          | swimming | climbing  | ice-hockey  | handball |
| Color   | emerald  | black | mauve | grey   |

