.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, swimming, skiing, biathlon
There 4 different types of food: peas, cranberry, mango, lemon
1. the person eating cranberry is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating peas is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
4. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating cranberry is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Sport   | swimming | cycling | skiing | biathlon  |
| Food     | cranberry   | peas  | lemon  | mango |

