.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
City: venice, liverpool, paris, london
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, september, december, march
1. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| City   | paris | london | venice | liverpool |
| Birthday           | march     | april     | december   | september         |

