.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, mechanic, doctor, dressmaker
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, alhambra, fonseca, old-henry
1. the coach is between the pall-mall-smoker and the mechanic##2
2. the doctor is on the far left or far right##3
3. the mechanic is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the dressmaker is on the left of the mechanic##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Job   | dressmaker | mechanic         | coach   | doctor |
| Cigar   | fonseca    | alhambra | old-henry | pall-mall   |

