.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, pink, grey, black
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bolivar, cain, vegafina
1. the vegafina-smoker is the person who likes grey##1
2. the cain-smoker is the person who likes emerald##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is the person who likes black##1
4. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
5. the person who likes emerald is in an even position##4
6. the person who likes grey is on the right of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Color   | pink | emerald | grey    | black |
| Cigar   | aristoff   | cain  | vegafina | bolivar     |

