.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, green, mauve, yellow
City: liverpool, edinburgh, marseilles, miami
1. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
2. the person who likes mauve is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who likes mauve##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person traveling to miami and the person traveling to marseilles##2
6. the person who likes green is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Color         | yellow   | mauve | purple | green    |
| City   | marseilles | edinburgh  | miami     | liverpool |

