.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, parkour, surfing, ice-hockey
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, analyst, entrepreneur, paramedic
1. the analyst is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the paramedic##1
5. the paramedic is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the entrepreneur is in an even position##4
7. the police-officer is the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | skateboarding    | surfing       | parkour |
| Job       | analyst  | entrepreneur | paramedic | police-officer  |

