.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, soul, rock, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, badminton, skiing, snowboarding
1. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of punk##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the fan of rock##1
5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | soul | rock | reggae  | punk |
| Sport     | volleyball      | skiing       | badminton | snowboarding     |

