.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, brown, lilac, ebony
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, march, september, july
1. the person who likes brown is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
3. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who likes black and the person who's birthday is in may##2
4. the person who likes brown is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Color         | black | lilac   | ebony | brown |
| Birthday   | july          | march | may         | september  |

 